      "endMs": 96280,
      "ipa": "ðə ˈhoʊl ˈθɪŋ.",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Toàn bộ.",
        "th": "ทั้งหมดเลย.",
        "id": "Semuanya.",
        "ar": "كل شيء."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69199f69b41f5ecfe3202ef6",
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Only the important parts.",
      "startMs": 96280,
      "endMs": 97360,
      "ipa": "ˈoʊnli ðə ɪmˈpɔːr.t̬ənt pɑːrts.",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Chỉ những phần quan trọng.",
        "th": "แค่ส่วนสำคัญเท่านั้น.",
        "id": "Hanya bagian-bagian penting.",
        "ar": "الأجزاء المهمة فقط."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69199f69b41f5ecfe3202ef8",
      "index": 47,
      "text": "Worst movie ever.",
      "startMs": 104380,
      "endMs": 106180,
      "ipa": "[ˈwɝst ˈmuːvi ˈɛvər.].",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Bộ phim tệ nhất từ trước đến nay.",
        "th": "หนังที่แย่ที่สุดเท่าที่เคยมีมา.",
        "id": "Film terburuk yang pernah ada.",
        "ar": "أسوأ فيلم على الإطلاق."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69199f69b41f5ecfe3202efa",
      "index": 48,
      "text": "Yeah, I almost walked out like 5 times.",
      "startMs": 106660,
      "endMs": 108500,
      "ipa": "ˈjɛə, ˈaɪ ˈɑlˌmoʊst ˈwɑkt ˈaʊt laɪk ˈfaɪv ˈtaɪmz.",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Vâng, tôi suýt bỏ đi khoảng 5 lần.",
        "th": "ใช่ ฉันเกือบจะเดินออกไปตั้ง 5 ครั้งแล้ว.",
        "id": "Ya, aku hampir keluar sekitar 5 kali.",
        "ar": "أجل، كدت أخرج حوالي 5 مرات."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "69199f69b41f5ecfe3202efc",
      "index": 49,
      "text": "How we doing?",
      "startMs": 108940,
      "endMs": 109340,
      "ipa": "ˈhaʊ wi ˈduːɪŋ?",
      "translations": {
        "vi": "Chúng ta thế nào rồi?",
        "th": "เราเป็นยังไงบ้าง?",
        "id": "Bagaimana kita?",
        "ar": "كيف حالنا؟?"
